{"tid":349174,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【田徑】保特獲12支足球隊邀試腳　經理人估計訓練後夠班踢英甲","createTime":"2017-08-06T10:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T17:51:59.000Z","uid":23058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb7936340fe397f07a648216a124d7d97f5770ae","tid":349174,"uid":23058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:49:59.000Z","msg":"以8月初世界田徑錦標賽為跑步最終戰的保特，不愁沒有出路。經理人已確認「牙買加閃電」將赴多蒙特跟操，更收到12支足球隊邀請試腳；經理人指，相信保特只要訓練6至9個月便有力出戰英甲。<br />\n<br />\n肯定與多蒙特跟操<br />\n<br />\n現年30歲的保特（Usain Bolt）是曼聯球迷的身份早已公開的秘密。經理人Ricky Simms向《每日星報》表示足球於保特心目中很重要︰「他一直談到足球，已收到12間球會邀請試腳，我不想透露這些球隊的名字，只肯定他會與多蒙特跟操，因為Puma的CEO是我們的好友，也是多蒙特的贊助。」人到中年由頂級跑手轉營為足球員，其經理人不算太樂觀︰「我不認為30歲的跑手能出戰英超或德甲，或者操練6至9個月後有望踢得上英乙或英甲。若我說他踢不到歐聯會被保特打頭，然而他這般富有及享有美滿的生活，不容易找到動力在雨中與預備組操練。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B7%91%E6%AD%A5/109225/-%E7%94%B0%E5%BE%91-%E4%BF%9D%E7%89%B9%E7%8D%B212%E6%94%AF%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83%E9%9A%8A%E9%82%80%E8%A9%A6%E8%85%B3-%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E4%BA%BA%E4%BC%B0%E8%A8%88%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E5%BE%8C%E5%A4%A0%E7%8F%AD%E8%B8%A2%E8%8B%B1%E7%94%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B7%2591%25E6%25AD%25A5%2F109225%2F-%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%25BE%2591-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%2589%25B9%25E7%258D%25B212%25E6%2594%25AF%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%2582%2580%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E8%2585%25B3-%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BC%25B0%25E8%25A8%2588%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E8%258B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B2&d=qmBGhWIfcDOk6vQx21bcvAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=fcae2ffd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B7%91%E6%AD%A5/109225/-%E7%94%B0%E5%BE%91-%E4%BF%9D%E7%89%B9%E7%8D%B212%E6%94%AF%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83%E9%9A%8A%E9%82%80%E8%A9%A6%E8%85%B3-%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E4%BA%BA%E4%BC%B0%E8%A8%88%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E5%BE%8C%E5%A4%A0%E7%8F%AD%E8%B8%A2%E8%8B%B1%E7%94%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n如果去英甲咪會見到戴俊偉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8a4b5161ae61e38781a3eab87c8bcb1309800b","tid":349174,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"做跑狗 有前途"},{"pid":"394e1ffee0a1d3eb67b35b7e80523bc9345eacc7","tid":349174,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"喺top gear講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a01a37a5e8224de24647389d024c8fa2c9bf861","tid":349174,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"做左右閘應該用得到<br />\n練下帶波可以係咁速度爆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958350f480e18ef5a7a00f6fcc9b48041f3044de","tid":349174,"uid":64525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"玩過fm都知低組別 最睇重速度同身體質素 Bolt兩樣都有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e074594c6189bee49f8149d8f3ff16187ef6c2e","tid":349174,"uid":47945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:13:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩過fm都知低組別 最睇重速度同身體質素 Bolt兩樣都有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩組別唔睇重呢兩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03bcec039ade64d546e54c33db32544a76aa89d0","tid":349174,"uid":3267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"咁似bale 不過30歲先黎搞 玩票性質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09949b05c5d6b1b8fa1d884eb50547257062877","tid":349174,"uid":73356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T